data.description: Beautiful Highland home with five bedrooms plus an office, backs up to the neighborhood walking trail with access from the backyard. The spacious living area opens to the dining area and island kitchen with breakfast bar, granite counters, stainless appliances along with a breakfast area. The first floor master suite features a master bath with dual vanity, garden tub, and separate shower. Second floor has a living area or gameroom along with three bedrooms. Great backyard with a covered patio. Community pool, clubhouse, parks, and much more!
